Name: Jandakot Rd, Banjup
Description: In the afternoon between 4 and 6pm, there is a queue of traffic ending at the Warton Rd roundabout. You can't see ahead, there are numerous blind corners. Trucks and cars use the road frequently. My concern, is being stuck in the queue with a truck travelling 80km/hr, or even a car, going around the bend, and all of a sudden, meeting the queue of cars. The traffic queue can be extremely long, past Cessna Drive. Sometimes, the issue occurs reverse direction in the morning, from freeway.
